Package ru.rusetskii.cashmachine.cash_operation

Class DenominationStorage

java.lang.Object
ru.rusetskii.cashmachine.cash_operation.DenominationStorage
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class DenominationStorage extends Object implements Cloneable
Represents banknotes of the specific currency stored by its denomination Is unit of a CashStorage class

Denomination Storage implements methods to work with its internal storage which is similar to CashStorage Also, class implements Cloneable interface to override clone() method so we can clone its field as well.

Author:
Nikita Rusetskii
